articles.author: Adam Cooper
articles.title: Sauber to run under Stake F1 Team name in 2024-25 - Motorsport.com
articles.description: The former Alfa Romeo Formula 1 outfit will run as Stake F1 Team Kick Sauber for the next two seasons, with Kick Sauber as the chassis name.
articles.content: Online gambling concern Stake will continue as title sponsor, while in addition streaming company Kick.com has stepped up its involvement and acquired the naming rights to the chassis, which will be … [+2144 chars]
